Elmah,io,is,an,error,tracking,service,that,allows,users,to,log,errors,in,the,cloud,Users,can,easily,search,through,their,error,logs,via,advanced,search,capabilities,and,the,level,of,access,that,individual,users,have,can,be,altered,based,on,their,role,Elmah,io,lets,users,hide,bugs,that,have,already,been,fixed,preventing,them,from,cluttering,up,the,log,but,not,actually,deleting,the,information,All,data,is,replicated,to,prevent,any,accidental,data,loss,Elmah,io,is,designed,for,mobile,accessibility,and,it,integrates,readily,with,popular,issue,trackers